Author: Douglas Nychka [aut, cre], Dorit Hammerling [aut]
Maintainer: Douglas Nychka <nychka@mines.edu>
Description: Embarrassingly parallel data analysis tasks
 in R are managed by a supervisor/worker model. The worker R
 sessions are creates and managed through the Rmpi package. 
Depends: R (>= 3.0), Rmpi
